WEBVTT

00:10.100 --> 00:11.550
News from Northern Equestria!

00:11.700 --> 00:13.550
Uh... your highness.

00:13.700 --> 00:14.330
Yes?

00:14.480 --> 00:18.280
I am simply to tell you that...
it has returned.

00:19.560 --> 00:21.330
Find Princess Cadance and Shining Armor.

00:21.480 --> 00:22.830
Yes, your highness.

00:25.630 --> 00:29.630
My dearest Twilight,
you must come to Canterlot at once.

